data.description: This beautiful well-maintained home is only four years old and comes with all the bells and whistles to save on initial ownership costs. Four spacious bedrooms and luxury vinyl plank floors throughout add consistency and easy maintenance to this open floor plan, making this home ideal for growing families. Located in the desirable Valley Ranch, take advantage of resort-like living right at home. This community hosts an amusement park style pool, playground, basketball and tennis courts, fitness center, and lake with fishing pier.  Find local shopping centers and major highways within 10 minutes.  Elementary school on-site with the Middle and High schools only 1 mile away.  Home conveys Washer & Dryer, Refrigerator, Elite Water Softener System, and backyard playset. Seller offering $5,000 towards closing costs with acceptable offer.
